    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a practical choice for a driver who values mechanical reliability over cosmetic perfection. The engine starts up without issue and the transmission shifts through all gears as expected, making it a dependable option for daily commuting. While the interior shows some visible wear and the exterior has a few minor scuffs and dings consistent with its age, the car remains structurally sound and safe to drive. It has been maintained to ensure all core systems are functional, offering a solid foundation for anyone needing a budget-friendly, honest vehicle.",
