    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This refined luxury sedan strikes the perfect balance between executive style and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, complemented by well-preserved alloy wheels and only the minor, expected signs of careful road use. Step inside to find a meticulously kept, smoke-free interior where the premium upholstery remains soft and the wood-grain accents are free of cracks. Every electronic feature, from the intuitive dual-zone climate control to the crisp surround-sound system, functions perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, backed by a consistent service history that ensures a confident driving experience. This is a complete package for a buyer seeking a high-end feel without the showroom price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
