      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks and feels great on the road? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really nice shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone who wants quality without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come on by and take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love it!",
