      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS service and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory-tuned composure with refreshed bushings, while the limited-slip differential provides excellent exit traction. Though the exterior shows light signs of use consistent with an active life on the road, the powertrain remains tight and responsive. A true enthusiast's specimen optimized for performance over concours presentation.",
